<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 20:07:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>这种大屠杀叙事迫使以色列人接受更少的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/this-holocaust-narrative-forces-israelis-to-settle-for-less/0000018f-5f23-d82e-a5df-7f33623f0000</link><description>不断提醒我们，犹太人民在大屠杀后奋起反抗，给予我们在恶劣环境下继续前行的力量。但这也迫使我们用太少的钱凑合</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 19:41:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/this-holocaust-narrative-forces-israelis-to-settle-for-less/0000018f-5f23-d82e-a5df-7f33623f0000</guid></item><item><title>反犹分子？反犹太复国主义者？一个更准确的术语，指的是希望以色列消失的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/anti-zionists-a-more-precise-term-for-pro-palestinian-protesters-who-want-israel-gone/0000018f-63b5-d284-adaf-77fda2890000</link><description>在 Reddit 上，我主要发现了有关 10 月 7 日和加沙战争的有趣且内容丰富的对话。直到一篇帖子让我大吃一惊，我无法忍住</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 19:39:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/anti-zionists-a-more-precise-term-for-pro-palestinian-protesters-who-want-israel-gone/0000018f-63b5-d284-adaf-77fda2890000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列士兵在加沙北部被爆炸装置炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-explosive-device-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-6398-d8a0-a3df-7bb8dfa90000</link><description>爆炸还造成一名军官和另一名战斗士兵受重伤，爆炸发生时部队正在加沙城南部的 Zeitoun 附近执行任务，而加沙南部的两名士兵则因反坦克火力而受重伤。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 18:24:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-by-explosive-device-in-northern-gaza/0000018f-6398-d8a0-a3df-7bb8dfa90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人不应该需要逮捕令来维持人性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-shouldnt-need-arrest-warrants-to-maintain-their-humanity/0000018f-635a-d3cc-a3ff-efda3c9c0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israelis-shouldnt-need-arrest-warrants-to-maintain-their-humanity/0000018f-635a-d3cc-a3ff-efda3c9c0000</guid></item><item><title>在拉法，人们在满目疮痍的沙漠中无处可逃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/in-rafah-people-flee-to-nowhere-in-a-desert-of-devastation-and-sand/0000018f-62b5-d8a0-a3df-7ab5e07b0000</link><description>大约 120 万加沙人挤在这座已经遭受毁灭性爆炸和炮击的城市里。他们确信拜登的警告不会阻止像加沙城和汗尤尼斯那样的大规模地面袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 17:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/in-rafah-people-flee-to-nowhere-in-a-desert-of-devastation-and-sand/0000018f-62b5-d8a0-a3df-7ab5e07b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 217 天：近东救济工程处称迄今为止已有 11 万人逃离拉法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-217-unrwa-says-110-000-have-fled-rafah-so-far/0000018f-635a-d9a0-a38f-ef7f90650001</link><description>WH：拜登政府尚未就向以色列运送武器做出最终决定 ■ CNN 报道，哈马斯要求停火 12 周，而不是以色列同意的六周 ■ 以色列坦克占领了拉法东部和西部的主要道路 ■ 内塔尼亚胡10 月 7 日称“政府的首要责任是保护人民……而人民却没有得到保护” ■ 这是战争进入 217 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 16:43:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-217-unrwa-says-110-000-have-fled-rafah-so-far/0000018f-635a-d9a0-a38f-ef7f90650001</guid></item><item><title>以色列不是土耳其或沙特阿拉伯，拜登打算保持这种状态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-turkey-or-saudi-arabia-and-biden-intends-to-keep-it-this-way/0000018f-6289-d9a0-a38f-eeaf3b620000</link><description>美国总统正试图阻止以色列成为一个被贱民国家，认为自己有义务维持两国之间的历史联盟。以色列领导人似乎完全无视这一使命</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 14:24:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-turkey-or-saudi-arabia-and-biden-intends-to-keep-it-this-way/0000018f-6289-d9a0-a38f-eeaf3b620000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡承认以色列政府在 10 月 7 日失败：“我对自己和每个人都坚持这一点”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-admits-israeli-government-failed-on-oct-7-i-hold-myself-and-everyone-on-this/0000018f-622c-d8a0-a3df-7a2c011e0000</link><description>以色列总理在接受菲尔·麦格劳博士采访时表示，“政府的首要责任是保护人民，这是最终的全面责任，但人民没有得到保护，我们不得不承认这一点”</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 12:16:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-admits-israeli-government-failed-on-oct-7-i-hold-myself-and-everyone-on-this/0000018f-622c-d8a0-a3df-7a2c011e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的根本冲突正在加沙战争中上演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-foundational-conflict-is-playing-out-in-the-gaza-war/0000018f-61ed-d9a0-a38f-edef3ed90000</link><description>下周，以色列将严肃地庆祝其独立，这是犹太复国主义的胜利，其意义本应得到解决。那么为什么争论仍然存在呢？</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 11:39:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israels-foundational-conflict-is-playing-out-in-the-gaza-war/0000018f-61ed-d9a0-a38f-edef3ed90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列示威者焚烧近东救济工程处东耶路撒冷大院；据报道“严重”损坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-demonstrators-torch-unrwa-east-jerusalem-compound-extensive-damage-reported/0000018f-61c4-d284-adaf-75fc34820000</link><description>警方表示，犯下这一行为的可能是低于刑事责任年龄的儿童，并表示，随着近东救济工程处要求以色列恢复“适当的安全”，他们将进一步调查；该机构负责人指示关闭该大楼，称其工人的生命处于危险之中</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 09:42:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/israeli-demonstrators-torch-unrwa-east-jerusalem-compound-extensive-damage-reported/0000018f-61c4-d284-adaf-75fc34820000</guid></item><item><title>首先，以色列高等法院命令警方调查西岸的非法定居点活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/in-first-high-court-orders-police-to-probe-illegal-settlement-activity-in-west-bank/0000018f-617a-d9a0-a38f-ed7fc5ba0000</link><description>这一决定是为了回应 2018 年的一份请愿书，要求西岸地区委员会调查其管辖范围内的非法建筑；政府并未否认有违章建筑</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 08:23:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/in-first-high-court-orders-police-to-probe-illegal-settlement-activity-in-west-bank/0000018f-617a-d9a0-a38f-ed7fc5ba0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡吹嘘以色列孤立无援，然后失去了美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-boasts-about-israel-standing-alone-then-loses-america/0000018f-5eba-d995-a5df-5ebf9ffd0000</link><description>“如果我们不保护自己，没有人会保护自己。如果我们必须孤立无援，我们就会孤立无援，”总理本周表示。这些言论的傲慢，仿佛以色列可以“独立”，只能与他对美国固有的忘恩负义相媲美。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-boasts-about-israel-standing-alone-then-loses-america/0000018f-5eba-d995-a5df-5ebf9ffd0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列的“末日武器”威胁绝非虚惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/bidens-doomsday-weapon-threat-to-israel-is-no-false-alarm/0000018f-5e5a-d9a0-a38f-fe7f46f20000</link><description>美国总统威胁停止向以色列运送进攻性武器，可能会削弱以色列北部军队的实力 ■ 人质协议谈判的分歧并不大，但很大程度上取决于政治考虑 ■ 内塔尼亚胡正中辛瓦尔和哈马斯的下怀正在重新控制拉斯维加斯大道</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/bidens-doomsday-weapon-threat-to-israel-is-no-false-alarm/0000018f-5e5a-d9a0-a38f-fe7f46f20000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 30 多枚火箭弹； 14枚火箭弹从加沙中部拉法发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-we-hope-to-overcome-disagreements-with-biden-but-we-will-protect-our-country/0000018f-6043-d8a0-a3df-7a635af70000</link><description>白宫：美国关切地关注以色列的拉法行动 ■ 哈马斯高级官员称内塔尼亚胡希望远方继续下去 ■ 以色列军队公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的四名士兵的名字 ■ 据报道，以色列国防军占领了拉法的主要道路，用坦克包围了该市的东半部</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 02:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-we-hope-to-overcome-disagreements-with-biden-but-we-will-protect-our-country/0000018f-6043-d8a0-a3df-7a635af70000</guid></item><item><title>“我第一次不想在维也纳街头说希伯来语”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-10/ty-article/.highlight/for-the-first-time-i-dont-want-to-speak-hebrew-on-the-streets-of-vienna/0000018f-5f3e-d9a0-a38f-ff3f4cb00000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位奥地利圣经考古学家前往以色列出差和度假，两名俄罗斯朝圣者前往耶路撒冷以神圣的方式庆祝生日</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 21:59:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-10/ty-article/.highlight/for-the-first-time-i-dont-want-to-speak-hebrew-on-the-streets-of-vienna/0000018f-5f3e-d9a0-a38f-ff3f4cb00000</guid></item><item><title>国家审计长：以色列军方要求推迟10月7日调查的要求不合理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/state-comptroller-israeli-militarys-demand-to-delay-october-7-probe-is-unreasonable/0000018f-5f20-d90e-a99f-7f7d82510000</link><description>马塔尼亚胡·恩格尔曼警告说，接受国防机构的立场可能会导致“在很长一段时间内无法对以色列国防军进行任何监督”，并妨碍获取关键证据</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 21:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/state-comptroller-israeli-militarys-demand-to-delay-october-7-probe-is-unreasonable/0000018f-5f20-d90e-a99f-7f7d82510000</guid></item><item><title>这些犹太裔波兰儿童梦想搬到以色列。大多数人死于大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/these-jewish-polish-boys-dreamed-of-moving-to-israel-most-died-in-the-holocaust/0000018f-5ed3-d9a0-a38f-fef718e90000</link><description>20 世纪 30 年代，犹太裔波兰学童用希伯来语写给他们心爱的老师（当时老师已前往巴勒斯坦）的信件在几十年后被发现，并收录在一本新书中。年轻人一心想在以色列土地上加入老师的行列，但大多数人在大屠杀中被杀害</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 20:53:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/these-jewish-polish-boys-dreamed-of-moving-to-israel-most-died-in-the-holocaust/0000018f-5ed3-d9a0-a38f-fef718e90000</guid></item><item><title>一名前往加沙拯救生命的美国神经外科医生的令人毛骨悚然的证词</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-chilling-testimony-of-a-u-s-neurosurgeon-who-went-to-gaza-to-save-lives/0000018f-5e8a-d995-a5df-5ebf2b890000</link><description>当所有能够逃离加沙的人都在这样做时，大卫·哈桑博士却进行了相反的旅程。他的故事是每个以色列人必读的</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 19:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-chilling-testimony-of-a-u-s-neurosurgeon-who-went-to-gaza-to-save-lives/0000018f-5e8a-d995-a5df-5ebf2b890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼抗议者封锁开往加沙的援助卡车</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-protesters-block-gaza-aid-trucks-from-jordan-bound-for-six-hours/0000018f-5e9a-d995-a5df-5ebf73570000</link><description>Tzav 9 组织的抗议者誓言要阻止援助直至所有人质获释，他们在米茨佩·拉蒙 (Mitzpe Ramon) 入口处封锁了 40 辆运往加沙的援助卡车。警方表示，他们没有收到以色列国防军关于卡车抵达的足够警告</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 18:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-protesters-block-gaza-aid-trucks-from-jordan-bound-for-six-hours/0000018f-5e9a-d995-a5df-5ebf73570000</guid></item><item><title>“这绝对是一场地震”：拜登、比比和武器禁运爆炸事件的美国高级专家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-09/ty-article/.highlight/definitely-an-earthquake-top-u-s-expert-on-biden-bibi-and-the-arms-embargo-bombshell/0000018f-5e38-d995-a5df-5e3f6cd50000</link><description>美国著名外交政策专家理查德·哈斯剖析了乔·拜登总统决定向以色列政府扣留威力炸弹背后的关键因素</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 18:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-09/ty-article/.highlight/definitely-an-earthquake-top-u-s-expert-on-biden-bibi-and-the-arms-embargo-bombshell/0000018f-5e38-d995-a5df-5e3f6cd50000</guid></item></channel></rss>